author: @Samantha-n3n
text: Man........its 2025 and i still watch this. He just poured out all his pain and emotion into the choreography. And it was only 2 minutes long. It should've been longer. He has worked so hard to get to where he is today, and he started with absolutely no training or experience. He just wanted people to notice his talent at the time, but no one did, as they only saw him as a pretty face. He was called a bully on multiple occasions, causing him to go on hiatus one of those times to self-reflect and wonder if he was a bad person :(. He portrayed Billie's song in the most emotional and talented way possible. It has me in a sobbing chokehold in the best way possible. We love you hyunjin, and not just because you have a pretty face, but we love you for your insane talent and skill!! 💗💗

author: @AnnaSénéchal
text:
hyunjin's note traduction:
I created the choreography for this song while remembering my most difficult moments.
First of all, the reason why I chose this song was because I was looking for a song that best fit the three themes of emptiness, despair and longing, and I thought that emptiness at the end of the party was the same feeling as the loneliness coming home after getting on a big stage and missing it because I did.
I tried to express my emotions as best I could and I hope I was able to convey them.

author: @Kot-2405
text:
@Kot-2405

И ДА!!!! Я не могу успокоиться. Настолько меня заклинило!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!! Надо знать творчество Хенджина, чтобы понимать и оценить  то, что он здесь конкретно, делает под Билли Айлиш: боль от любви и она с большой буквы, потому как, очень больно, ведь она односторонняя/безответная ( а Хенджин, совсем молоденький и знать еще ведь не знает о любви, и мудрости жизненной у него пока нет). Как так он передает глубину танца и его эмоции? Я просто схожу с ума, получая наслаждение, прямо эмоциональный оргазм. 
Для Кореи- это просто редкая жемчужина, я бы сказала бриллиант!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!! 
Давно у меня не было такого восхищения. 
В Индии- Это Ритик Рошан и Тайгер Шрофф, и пока никому не удалось их в мастерстве переплюнуть, 
в Корее- это Хенджин, которого я недавно открыла, 
в Китае- Ван Ибо, который собственно танцу учился именно в Корее.

author: @katarinaregasova4001
text:
Hello Hyunjin,
my name is Katka and I am saying this as a person to another person (not to an idol, because we have the same amount of worth as humans ;)).
Actually, I hope that you can read this, because I believe, God would like to tell you something.
If it would be possible, I wouldn’t type this so openly, but you know - you are kinda ”person for all” (everybody can know things about you) and “person for nobody” (not many can know your personal email;)).
So to not waste yout time: I would like you to meet my God! :) Why? Because: 
1. Although you are always with people (even more like you would like to be;)), you can feel alone at times and that pain starts to be visible, as you try to convey her…
2. You are doing your job, which is inspiring and awesome, but sometimes it can feel like it is just a regullar job (or worse, like you must serve other peoples expectacions and that’s not fun, nor freedom and it is hard to be yourselve in that position. Like, nobody out there really doesn’t know the real you and you yourselve are just trying to know you more…:)). And maybe it starts to feel a bit…empty/worthless. Like the things you do really don’t have a higher purpose? I bet you wanna change the world for better. And now, when you have all the means to do it, you are kind of stuck… Like, you are this hiiiigh level artist and what comes from it? Where is the “thing” why you were pursuing perfection? Why are som many people fake? Why is this just not enough inside of your heart? There may still be a few posh dreams of what to achieve, but the world and art in it are just not enough to fill that desire of being loved by someone and have real meaning…?… 
Once I was at the simmilar spot, although I am not a famous person at all…actually, I like it that way and am freed from wanting to be famous. :) At first, I thought that I must be famous, otherwise I can’t do what I love (=art) and live from it (=earning money:)). But somebody changed me (=yep, it was Jesus:)). At first, I have had a relationship with a nice boy and we were maddly in love. My wishes were fullfilled, I felt like I don’t need anything else… BUT we are humans and the love we can “do by ourselves” is not perfect at all. (It crushed after 4 years and it was a happy ocasion to be free again, otherwise I wouldn’t have such an awesome husband now;)).
But then I’ve met God - the real only one mighty awesome God full of miracles in my room. (more about Him is in the Bible). I won’t tell you what you allready heard about Jesus, just want to pray for you, if you don’t mind:
“God, let Hyunjin get to know you personally. Let him know You when he is alone in his room and there is dark and he needs somebody who really understands. Somebody, who actually knows everything and who loves him like nobody ever will, the way he is right now. Show him your thoughts about him and let him be free from all fears and masks… let him feel your warmth, let him know that you are ALWAYS with him and you know what he needs and You are willing to give it to him. Please, give him goosebumps as he reads this and talk to him again in his dreams, as how you did it before. Oh and show him why You have made him the way he is and what is his purpose;). In Jesus name, may he be filled with the Holy Spirit and real joy and peace and truth forever. Amen.”

See ya in heaven, hopefully ;)

author: @SitSTAYgoodgrl
text: As a modern dance piece this is just brilliant. It’s dense and layered. It’s telling a story like most contemporary dance pieces, yes. But the way he weaves different styles of movement together effortlessly is just brilliant. I always disliked most contemporary dance (as a dancer), because it felt like dances use “feeling the music” as an excuse for simplistic choreography. But this was both technical and emotional.

O nível de perfeição contida aqui é imensurável... O Hyunjin transcende a arte da dança levando a ela sua doce alma em cada gesto. E essa música fala muito além do que quer dizer, ela é intensa e eu me vejo nela quase sempre. I love you Hyunjin and please always know that no matter what you faces in this life, no one can ever be you, no one can replace you, you are the best you and the only you. You are perfect and you brings out the best in everything you do. And don't feel too lonely because I love you unconditionally, even when the world may forget you and move on, I will always remember you, love you and support you. Our worlds maybe different, when it's night here it's day there, when it's day here it's night there, we may be strangers but I accept we are both human under the same sun, moon and stars. If destiny allows us to meet someday, a day I hoped for, then I will tell you all the beautiful things you would love to hear🌹💐❤.

text:
Today is exactly 3 years since that terrible day...
Please, my love, never leave again... Don't disappear... Don't leave us. Please always warm us with your warmth and know that we are always there, we love you, no matter what happens, you will always find a secluded safe place in our hearts. Please be happy and healthy, conquer the whole world, you deserve all its love and even more...
I will never forgive your haters for everything that happened to you. Please let's STAY together and try to make sure this never happens again 💔💔💔 Love of Stay is with you forever Hyunjinnie ❣

author: @aleiru1097
text:
Сегодня ровно 3 года с того ужасного дня...
Пожалуйста, любимый, никогда больше не уходи... Не исчезай... Не оставляй нас. Пожалуйста, всегда согревай своим теплом и знай, что мы всегда рядом, мы любим тебя, что бы ни случилось, ты всегда найдёшь укромное безопасное место в наших сердечках. Пожалуйста, будь счастлив и здоров, завоюй весь мир этот мир, ты заслуживаешь всей его любви и даже больше... 
Никогда не прощу за всё, что с тобой произошло. Пожалуйста, давай будем вместе и постараемся, чтобы это больше никогда не случилось 💔💔💔 Любовь Стэй с тобой навсегда, Хёнджинни ❣

author: @user-wk5tp8ii6c
text:
私的メモ

【ヒュンジンのコメント】 私が一番大変だった時を思い出してこの曲の振り付けを作りました。 まず、この曲を選んだ理由は、空虚さ、絶望感、懐かしさ、これら3つのテーマに最もよく似合う曲を探し、パーティーが終わった時の空虚さが大きな舞台に上がった後、それを恋しくして家に帰った時の孤独のような感情だ。思ったからです。 できるだけ感情を表現しようと努力し、伝えられたことを願っています。

author: @rihyuu
text: This really made me tear up (still having tears in my eyes). My number one rule is and has always been, if something's REALLY good, I express my emotions and cry for example. This choreo resonates with me on an emotional level, the song "when the party's over" already hits me with reality, but this choreo, made by an amazing individual whose talent is so exceedingly beautiful to me (and many more stays), adds another level of reality and emotion towards me. How Hyunjin has the ability to portrait such emotion is still beyond me, it's kinda like Hyunjin discovered a missing piece to this song by choreographing to it. I absolutely LOVE this, no matter how many tears I shall cry, music has always been my comfort zone, my reasoning to keep going, so please, take it from me, don't give up, if you love music and maybe also connect to music, listen to it. It does help, and things will get better if it's currently tough for you, ok? <3

Great job Hyunjin!!

text:
Just translating [Hyunjins Comment]:
I created the choreography for this song while thinking of the most difficult times for me.
First of all, the reason I chose this song was to search for the song that best fits the three themes of emptiness, despair, and longing, and I thought that the feeling of emptiness at the end of the party was the same feeling as loneliness when returning home, missing it after going on a big stage. because it did
I tried to express my feelings as much as possible, and I hope it was delivered.

author: @annamoon929
text: Дорогой Хёнджин, ты не представляешь насколько сильно я люблю тебя (и skz в целом, конечно же❤️)... Твое владение телом в танце так завораживает, твой голос также имеет свою изюминку, что в рэпе, что в вокале прекрасно раскрывается из раза в раз✨ То, сколько труда в это всё вложено, вызывает восхищение. Я знаю, что все ребята очень много трудятся, чтобы показать лучший результат stay, что порой даже представить сложно. И я просто хочу надеяться, что вы все хорошо о себе заботитесь🤍 Пожалуйста, будьте здоровы, stay этого очень хотелось бы! Спасибо за ваш труд, я каждый раз очень благодарна! Как жаль, что не могу выразить вам всю любовь... Вы все невероятные и такие замечательные люди, со своими переживаниями, страхами, со своим проявлением любви и творчества💕 Спасибо, что остаётесь с нами, а мы останемся здесь для вас🤲💖

author: @skylar5823
text:
天呐我竟然今天才看这个舞 这竟然是我看他的自编舞里最立马感到强烈共鸣以至眼泪即将落下 所有的情感在肢体表现中淋漓尽致 喷薄而出 不断回味后内心一层层地悲伤又一层层自我安慰
这极致延展的线条 刚柔并济的肢体 融入音乐又通过音乐表现的强烈情感实在太爱了 真的是舞蹈艺术的魅力😭两年前的你就已经如此厉害了 真心希望以后的平常是更多的快乐 情感就宣泄在舞蹈和绘画中吧😭

author: @chaeyeonology
text:
Translated version of Hyunjin's comment: 
I made the choreography of this song thinking about the most difficult times for me. First of all, I chose this song because I thought that emptiness, despair, longing, and emptiness at the end of the party were the same feelings as loneliness when I came home missing it after going on a big stage. I tried to express my feelings as much as I could, and I hope it was delivered.

TRADUCCION DEL COMENTRIO QUE ACOMPAÑA ESTA COREOGRAFIA:Creé la coreografía de esta canción pensando en los momentos más difíciles para mí.
En primer lugar, la razón por la que elegí esta canción fue para buscar la canción que mejor encajara con los tres temas de vacío, desesperación y añoranza, y pensé que el sentimiento de vacío al final de la fiesta era el mismo sentimiento de soledad. cuando volvía a casa, lo echaba de menos después de subir a un gran escenario.

author: @chickenswag353
text:
so i know this video is over two years old by now, but i wanna give my take on this choreography! i'm not a professional or know anything about dance, but i haven't seen many comments talking about what this choreography may be sharing.



so to start, hyunjin's comment in the description. he talks about how he made this choreo during a really difficult time for him, and how it has themes of emptiness, despair, and longing. and the one of those that i noticed the most in the video is longing. some moments where that can really be seen are 0:42 , 1:16 , 1:34 (this one especially), and the rest after 2:09. in these, you can really see the longing in his movements. i pointed out 1:34 because that's when you can really see it. it's almost like he's chasing after something.

my personal interpretation of this dance is wanting something (or someone) bad for you. it's about being used by someone, yet still longing for their presence despite how much they hurt you. 0:59 seems to be a rather uh sensual part of the dance. this makes me think it might have been a bad romantic relationship, but don't come at me cause i'm not gonna assume anything.

in other parts where his body just kind of "flops" (1:31 specifically), it reminds me of a puppet on strings. again, themes of being used. and at 0:48 i think the pat on the shoulder is suppose to show comfort? perhaps having to comfort himself or being comforted by whoever or whatever was harming him. because at the end of the day, sometimes the things that hurt us the most are the ones we find the most comfort in.

in the beginning (0:22), his hand reaches forward only for him to use his other to pull it away. we see this again at 2:09. it makes me think that he's restraining himself in a way. his hand is blindly reaching around, trying to grasp onto something, and he has to pull that hand away. after this is when i really began to notice the emptiness he mentions in his comment. the last move (when his hands move away from each other), i think it shows that whatever was left in him has dissolved, leaving empty air.

if you really really take note, you see hyunjin put his hands around his neck a lot in the video. maybe i'm looking just a wee bit too far into it, but maybe this shows the feeling of suffocating in this relationship? that's how a lot of people describe it, so that's what comes to my mind. at 1:40, he makes a motion of taking a call and then puts his hand around his throat. i think perhaps he received a call that left him feeling like he was suffocating? or maybe he just added it in idk.

finally, hyunjin's song choice. in his comment, he said he looked for a song that best fit the themes of the choreo and his feelings. "when the party's over" is about...take a guess....being in a toxic relationship. one that leaves you with an emptiness but also longing. this kind of further makes me believe this choreo tells the story of a possible bad relationship. could be platonic or romantic, or even with anything that's generally bad for you.

as of right now, hyunjin has written songs that explore this theme. taste and ice.cream are the ones that come the mind. this is a very beautiful choreography, and i hope hyunjin is doing well! this is just my personal interpretation of the dance, but i'm open to any other ideas tbh. stay well :D

author: @zeenatei3790
text: Although I always understood this song, and the emptiness and delicateness of her vocals and pain in the lyrics, I never had any emotional connection to this song.  But not even 30 seconds into Hyunjin's choreography, and I am literally bawling my eyes out.   The amount he speaks without using words is indescribable.  For me, he capture the essence of the song more than BE did herself.  A new Stay, binge watching as many of the old episodes, MV's, behind the scenes and everything else I can get my hands on.  These young men have taken me on such an enjoyable roller coaster of laughter, light, care, consideration, silliness and compassion, but this truly shattered my emotions into a million tiny shards of pain.  Only someone who has know true pain, could convey what Hyunjin just did.  Truly masterfully beautifully Hyunjin in his element.

The hand moving from a phone to chocking him as the head ticks as the time passes by is such a simple motion but the sharp actions and intent with the context of the song just write the song so beautifully. author: @camiivavi
text:
escribi esto hablando del video con un amigo y no me pude expresar mejor asi que aqui esta: 
cuando vi ese video y encima me dijeron su significado no pude evitar sentir un nudo en la garganta me transmitia demasiadas cosas,amor,pasion,tristeza,temor,miedo,panico,tensión,anehlo la "venda" de fanatismo que tenia de decir "ay hyunjin que bonito" y ya,se fue esfumando por cada minuto que pasaba al ver el video cada paso es una palabra en una historia por contar son sentimientos por expresar solo pude ver a una persona bailando,no vi a el idol de kpop que quiero mucho o a hwang hyunjin de stray kids eso es lo que amo de su baile,del baile en general que puede hacer que te centres en los movimientos de algo y hacerte reflexionar sobre lo que te hace sentir
no ves a una persona en especifico,ves emociones,ves sentimientos al inicio es de que "aja un bailecito" pero viendo mas me encanto como podia contar tanto con tan pocas cosas

lo senti como una forma de liberación
en ese video hay un paso donde hyunjin se da como una especie de palmaditas en la espalda
y dios,lo unico que pude hacer fue llorar y llorar
hyunnie no estaba haciendo nada mas que un paso de baile,pero lo que me transmitia era demasiado fuerte,cuando tiembla las piernas,cuando hace esos movimientos con las manos como de frustracion,el paso de las manos en el cuello dios mio,al verlo solo me podia encontrar con miles de lagrimas recorriendo mi rostro...

author: @iltelelee7650
text: хочу поделится своими впечатлениями от этого видео.каждый раз когда мне становится плохо морально , когда я ухожу в себя ,я всегда почему то возвращаюсь к этому видео…я не понимала чем мне так оно нравится .сегодня ,вновь смотря этот танец у меня в голове появилось много мыслей .мне показалось что я могу прочитать танец , как бы странно это не звучало …я чувствую то что ты  хотел передать.хочу сказать спасибо  твоему творчеству,я не знаю почему ты не можешь понять за что тебя люди любят…вспоминаю твои слова на недавнем концерте в сеуле,которые ты говорил на последний день …просто знай что ты вдохновляешь многих людей на совершение чего то нового,ты даёшь им веру в себя ,меня поражает то  как ты увлечён  рисованием…ты совершенствуешься с каждым днём и не перестаёшь  этим заниматься …я поражена…спасибо тебе хенджин за мотивацию …глупо это писать сюда ведь ты этого не увидишь ,но может некоторые стэй увидят моё сообщение и возьмут из него что нибудь для дальнейшей жизни .желаю тебе сил и здоровья !еще раз спасибо!

author: @h-playwithmyhart.4806
text: Hyunjin. It was certainly your musicality that drew me to you first. You have such a playful but easy tone which highlights and gives definition to every Stray Kids song. You don’t have fixated or set rapping style. You are very experimental vocally and lyrically and I’ve found myself charmed by your voice due the versatility of it. I also love your singing style for similar reasons. You are just as diverse of a singer as you are rapper. It is really peaceful and harmonious; and blends perfectly with the rest of your members. I love how you don’t hold anything back when you’re singing and I can really feel the emotion and work that you pour into each line that you sing. Similarly to your singing and rapping, your body knows no limits when you are met with a choreography. You dance with a ferocity and a passion that no other performers can possess. You take each choreography and sincerely make it your own, which is honestly a blessing to watch. When you are dancing, you can be yourself and express your emotions with the beauty of your body movements. You can lose yourself easily into your dance and you are so comfortable and trusting of your own abilities. For this generation specifically, you have transformed music and given new meaning to what it can and should do for people. You are changing the world each day that you continue to share your artistry and dance; and we are so lucky to be alive right now to get to be a part of the history that you’re making. At the same time that I love your music and dance, I love your personality as well. I love that sometimes you keep to yourself, but other times, you are goofy and outgoing. As I mentioned before, you are extremely freeing to be around and those who spend time with you can relax and be themselves in your presence. I know that nobody can attest to these qualities quite like your members. Seven different personalities, and they all love you and cherish you for their own special reasons. They’ve looked to you and have modeled their perseverance off of how you strive to not let the difficult times hold you down and prevent you from success. You have opened your heart up to all seven people, although you come from different backgrounds, and that has encouraged them to all to have such a loving relationship with one another. You’ve had love for them since you began your journey with them and this has establishing a lifelong love that all of you had before you even debuted. You see the beauty and necessity of every single member and constantly remind them how important they are to Stray Kids. There is likely no greater feeling for them than knowing that they have you by their side if they don’t have anything else. The most important takeaway is the time they spend with you and the way you make them feel, and these are both filled with warm memories they can take with them for the rest of their lives. You’ve already spent some of the happiest and life-changing moments of your life with them, and there is still more to come. The members of Stray Kids, also your brothers and your family, couldn’t have somebody who loves them any more than you do to look after them. You are always so considerate of them and their feelings and respond to them however they need. They are the best versions of themselves because of you and because you love them just the way they are. Now, they can go on to do whatever they aspire to because you’ve encouraged them with that confidence. I want to personally thank your parents and family for raising you and helping you become the person you are today. I know they mean a lot to you, and that you couldn’t be here doing what you are without their love and support. Because of them, you can use your platform to share with the world the same love that they have provided you with your whole life. I hope you never forget that they are always going to be the most proud of you no matter what you do. They love you most in this world and they do so in a way that nobody else understands. Stay love them as you do and we keep them in our hearts as we continue our time with you. We are so grateful to them for bringing you into the world, and for changing the world the same way that you do. Hyunjin, you touch each individual heart of every Stay, and this is easily one of the most charming parts about you. It is in your nature to make each and every Stay feel special, even if you don’t know us personally. You welcome Stay from all around the world with open arms, and I felt as if I was a part of the family my whole life. You are so dedicated to your Stay and this is very apparent in everything that you do, whether it be performing or communicating with us directly. You have so much compassion for Stay and I feel like we are existing in our own separate world with you. Although we all live in different areas across the world, you take us to a place where we can all be one big family together, and it is one of the greatest feelings in the world. What you give to us is irreplaceable, and there could never be another person who helps us see the worth in ourselves the way you do. You also help us love one another. You influence others to treat others with kindness and I’ve met some of the most heartwarming Stay. I know that you help this family become closer every single day, and you remind us that if we have nothing else, we have each other. You invite us into your heart, the same way that you do your members, and you see qualities in us that we don’t even see ourselves. I know for a fact that there are Stay who only believe in themselves because of you. You also share so much of yourself with us, and this is perhaps one of the biggest ways you can show somebody that you trust. As time goes on, I notice you revealing more of yourself through your music and just through direct conversation with your Stay. You have gotten so personal with us and this lets us know just how much you actually believe in us and trust us to keep these parts of you within our hearts. There is no greater honor than to have you place this vulnerable side of you in our hands, and we want to do the same for you. I know that it is not always easy to do this, so I hope you know that we could never mislead you or betray your trust if we wanted to. You are one of the most generous people we know, and we could not be here giving love to others and to you without the love that you gave us first. I know that you’ve been through a lot, both personally, and professionally, and that your time as an idol has not always been easy or enjoyable. You’ve been active for some time now, but during your training period alone, you’ve been met with demanding expectations, which many people cannot even say they’ve undergone. Just as your family is, Stay could not be more proud of you from overcoming your hardships and making it out on the brighter side. Each time you are met with a grueling time or task, thought it make time, you eventually endure through it until the end, and become more experienced. As Stay, I can say we learn so much from how you choose to release stress or convey how you’re feeling through the mediums that provide you comfort.  We are beyond proud of you and continue to learn from you each day. I hope that this birthday makes all of your dreams come true, and you can take the time to truly celebrate who you are as a person. I know it might be difficult to focus on yourself, and if you find this to be the case, I hope you leave it to those who surround you and your admiring fans from all across the world to help you realize how revolutionary of a person you are. You are truly a gifted musician, and a courteous and selfless individual. You deserve this day, and every day that follows, to feel as appreciated as you truly are. I hope that every second is filled with memories that are unforgettable, and that this will be one of the greatest days that you’ve had! Please have fun and celebrate in whatever way you choose, because your Stay will be cheering with you!  Thank you for sacrificing your time, efforts, pain, doubt, fear, tears, emotions, and physical boundaries just to bring us any content at all. For every effort that you put in that you might think is small, a Stay’s mood or day is completely changed for the better. You are blessing to this world and continue to change it every day with how you choose to heal it and the people living in it. I hope you don’t overwork yourself because you are perfect just the way you present yourself to us. We will support you and be there for you for the rest of our lives! I pray that you and your loved ones stay safe, and find happiness and worth in the future. Happy birthday Hyunjin, and we adore you so much!!!

author: @0ne_B1llion
text:
Hyunjin’s facial expressions are magnificent. He changed facial expressions and emotions from cute, sexy, devilish smile, sultry gazed, the way he shuts his eyes and flings himself blind into it, raging , fiery, demonic , sexy, hot all engaged with his graceful movements and synchronous with music. His stage performance is just insanely beautiful. His sharp movements , body controls, his kinetic energy flow yet it’s so powerful and magnificent. When Hyunjin dances, he crosses that boundary between human and immortal, glittering like stars and diamonds, like obsidian under the earth. He takes the audience and chokes them on their own love, their own lust. I can’t take my eyes off of him even just for a second. He has the power to get me so emotional. I fall for him over and over again. Hyunjin’s an artist’s masterpiece.  
But then when he’s off of the stage. Hyunjin’s probably the softest out of all Stray Kids members. He’s all gooey , lovely, gentle and sensitive. Everything his members feel, he feels just as keenly. Hyunjin’s such a terrible liar. Everything that happens to him written all over his face. He cried the most among of the rest members and He cries whenever his members cry. Because everything he feels is like lightning inside him. Hyunjin’s genuine , pure, soft and cluelessly adorable. That’s why they love him so much. Han said Hyunjin has fragile mentally like glass. And then Seungmin added, It’s not glass but almost like snow crystals. It shatters the moment it drops. Hyunjin’s on his sentimental side. He got controlled by his emotions very often. And Chan said, Hyunjin clearly knows wha he likes and what he dislikes. He’ll firmly show it. Because Hyunjin’s really honest . He’s really honest about his feelings. He’s the type who expressed everything. He’s really honest and innocent. He could be naïve because he’s too innocent. Hyunjin also endearing and working the way too hard because he means everything he does and he’s kinda dumb about it. He doesn’t know how to be anything other than himself, he confronts everything he encounters with the same sincere self and a lot of the time. Because he’s really genuine, innocent, honest, pure and sincere. He really wanted to love to be loved and affection from stay and his members.  
So that’s why I want to tell this to all stay. When Hyunjin loves us , it means he really meant it. He really loves us , stay. He really does. He’s sincere , honest and true. And stay, Remember when Our leader Bang Chan said “ I don’t think anyone can beat Hyunjin’s visuals”. I’m sure he meant Hyunjin’s not just handsome or beautiful outside, but inside too. Hyunjin’s like a real Angel. He’s so pure that I’m crying so hard. It doesn’t matter He doesn’t know me , he doesn’t know us personally. As long as he knows we’re stay. Who’ll always be with him , be with Stray Kids forever.  We’re so lucky to have Someone like Hyunjin, we’re lucky to have Stray Kids. They’re loving and warm just like our Hyunjin. 
Me , myself, I love him so much more than anything. I love Stray Kids so much. Some people might say I’m day dreaming or whatever. I don’t care. I’m really happy to love him, to love stray kids and support them as much as I could. And let Stray Kids know that they’re Loved. And one thing that I know, I love them and They love me , they love stay sincerely. That’s the most important thing. And I never once regret to be a Stay. This is the first time I love and treasure a boyband so much. I was a fan of multiple boy bands but never once Gotten me so emotionally like I do to Stray Kids. I’ll be forever Stay. This is my final bond promise as a forever fan. #Straykids #Hyunjin #Bangchan #Leeknow #Changbin #Hanjisung #Seungmin #Felix #Jongin  #Stay #Lovestay

author: @marianapecas4822
text:
hwang hyunjin you're a true artist. it's been more than a year since ive commented here but today watching you felt different. "empty" that word broke me at the end, because after seeing you dance i felt empty, i felt breatheless, underwater. but at the same time, my brain experienced the fulfilling experience of seeing you express your emotions through your other language, and there's nothing empty about that.
you're a true artist because you leave me thinking whether emptiness is good or not, you're a true artist because you speak through art. your body speaks through dance, your voice speaks through music, you speak your mind and thoughts through your drawings and paintings. you're a true artist and role model.

author: @brennak5044
text:
UGH the feel of this whole video and choreo is ✨ I M P E C C A B L E ✨

I think one of my fav things about this video is that he doesnt look at the camera and heres why: In Play With Fire he uses his expressions to really add character and emotion to the preformance. His intimidating fierce expressions in that video really give this feeling of a caged animal, something dangerous fighting to break free. That was incredible and greatly added to the performance. 

BUT IN THIS VIDEO. I can only assume it was completely intentional that he doesnt look at the camera since it doesnt even happen once. I dont know if that was Hyunjins idea or whoever directed the shooting of the video itself but either way, i love it. The fact that Hyunjin never looks at the camera gives this video a feeling of quiet and melancholy intimacy. Its almost feels like you arent watching a performance so much as a moment in someone life that you are just a fly on the wall for. It really hammers home the sad and vulnerable feeling of this video.

author: @brennak5044
text:
Okay. Im back here after some time and i have some WORDS.

This is the video that single handedly made me a Stay. 
Ive been a kpop fan for many many years now but no group has ever grabbed my attention so fully and so suddenly like SKZ. I listen to a ton of groups music casually and follow some of their activity but i mostly just consider myself an Army through and through. UNTIL NOW. I clicked on this video and i was absolutely floored by his talent. I had no idea that SKZ had such talented dancers. It all started with this video and then i was falling down a hole of anything related to Hyunjins dancing. Criminal, Play With Fire, Hyunjin's Practice Room comps, fancams, i was inhaling everything i could find. And then dance practices led to music videos, led to funny moments, led to SKZ Vlogs, basically anything i could find. 
Im still pretty new and im still learning but, very fittingly, im here to stay now. These guys are some of the most talented, genuine, hardworking, funny people ive ever seen. They've come to mean a great deal to me very quickly. Hyunjin will always have a special place in my heart because he introduced me to stray kids. I feel like Skz is going to have an incredible amount of success in the future and im so excited to see how they grow.

author: @joselyn8417
text:
Hyunjin es mucho más que una simple cara bonita. Él es demasiado talentoso, se ha esforzado mucho para mejor su baile, para poder expresarse mejor a través de la danza, aparte también a trabajado mucho su rendimiento vocal además que él también compone canciones, él sin duda tiene muchísimo talento que merece ser más reconocido.

Tiene una hermosa voz que te tranquiliza, un estilo para el rap que te hace mover la cabeza cada que rapea, su baile te deja hipnotizado y cautivado. Todo él es un reflejo del talento que de por sí tiene y de lo mucho que trabajo para mejorar, so-  a lo que quiero llegar es que el merece más que un simple "Te amo",  pedimos que reconozcan su talento pero ni siquiera los mismos fans lo hacen, no cuesta nada reproducir sus players. Hay que devolverle la felicidad que él nos da.

author: @leticiavargas1136
text:
안녕 baby 🤍
잘 잤어?
You slept so late I hope you could have a good night of rest. 

What're the plans for today?
Are you having fun practicing?
I'm.. looking forward to see you performing... 🙈 

You easily could be one of my best friends, do you know that?
This little space in the world right here when I'm talking to you...
Thank you. 

If you have ever read anything, If you ever waited for anything of mine... If you ever thought how would it be things in a different situation... 

I can only be thankful to you.
As I can come and talk, I wish you could do that too.
I'd listen every TMI and every worries of yours. Maybe you wouldn't even have to say it... I can easily notice looking into your eyes.. That's ok just be by your side.
I'll always be. 

Love you,
With all my heart. 

Yours,
Joy.

text:
I watched this so many times while Hyunjin wasn’t performing this year and marveled at how great the choreography was and how much I missed seeing him dance … then he comes back and drops Play With Fire in my lap and I am blown away. This dance is fabulous, but the growth he’s shown in his technique and ability since this was released is astounding. He’s a truly motivated and talented young man with many years of performance in front of him. 

Hyunjin I am so glad to see you again!

Translation of Hyunjin’s message:
[Hyunjin's Comment] I made the choreography for this song while remembering the most difficult time. I tried to express my feelings as much as possible, and I hope it was delivered.
———————

author: @milagrosaguero7953
text:
cuando escuchaba esta canción estaba muy lastimada tanto mental como emocional y psicológicamente, la había dejado de escuchar por un tiempo larguísimo. la primera vez que vi después de mucho tiempo este player me enamoró su forma de bailar, podía interpretar el dolor que sentía y el que me transmitía la canción. siempre que lo veo rompo en llanto y demuestra el poder que tiene como bailarín y artista. fue la primera persona que lograba transmitir tan bien esto y seguir viendo cosas así dentro del grupo me daba un mimo al alma. 
quería contar esto mientras lo veía nuevamente, porque este player es una de las cosas más hermosas que alguna vez vi

text:
No sabes cuanto te extraño, hace 3 años te conocí, y fue el mejor día de mi vida, tu me sacaste adelante, me diste ánimos cuando más lo necesitaba, tu pintaste mi vida de un color amarillo, la viniste a mejorar, gracias a tí ahora tengo una razón para seguir adelante y nunca más darme por vencida como lo hacia antes, todo en mi vida era perfecto junto a tí, pero..... cuando te fuiste.... sentí una sensación horrible, es algo que no se puede explicar, el dolor, las noches solas y tristes, con la esperanza de que vuelvas, me estoy derrumbando poco a poco y se que volveras, lo sé.... cuanto daria por estar contigo y decirte que todo estará bien, todo pasará y volverá a como era antes, que no tengas miedo, nunca estarás solo, yo siempre te apoyare y estaré contigo, porque te amo Hyunjin, me tienes loca por tí, eres una de las pocas personas que me hace sentir una sensación rara en mi estomago.... te amo y siempre lo haré, hasta el ultimo dia de mi vida, y en la otra si se puede, eres unico y perfecto a tu manera, espero que estes bien, cuidate mi empanadita, mi color rosa, mi esperanza...... mi little star.

그래서 공연 끝나고 마지막의 마지막까지 남아서 
엔딩 크레딧 나오고 

스탭들의 퇴장 지시가 있기까지 
그 공간에 더 머물다 나오는 편인데.
하물며 무대 위의 너는 더 크게 느끼겠지.

공연장에서 나와 일상으로 돌아오는 과정이 
공연 자체가 스페셜한 경험이란 걸 다시 깨닫고 
다시 그 스페셜한 경험을 하기 위해 
일상을 치열하게 살아가는 거 아닐까 싶어.

그 치열한 일상을 살아갈 힘을 주는 존재인 너에게,
반대로 이젠 내가 힘을, 에너지를 전해주고 싶어.

다시 오프에서 공연할 그 날까지,
치열한 일상을 힘차게 살아갈테니,
너의 일상에도 에너지가 넘치기를 바란다구...

author: @leticiavargas1136
text:
안녕 baby, 어떻게 지내제요?
일요일이야!
날씨가 어때요? 그것을 즐기십시오! 재미있는 일을하세요.
날씨가 좋으면 밖으로 나가서 공기를 좀 마시세요. 여기 추워요.
그래도 괜찮아 눈을 감고 너를 생각할 수있어 ... 그럼 더 따뜻해 질게. 

"I find shelter in this way
Under cover, hide away
Can you hear when I say
I have never felt this way
...
Could I be, was I there
It felt so crystal in the air
I still want to drown whenever you leave
Please teach me gently how to breathe 

And I'll cross oceans like never before
So you can feel the way I feel it too
And I'll send images back at you
So you can see the way I feel it too" 

이 노래는 Shelter by Bird라고합니다.
아까 듣고 추천 할까 생각했는데 ...
언젠가 내 감정이 당신에게 닿기를 바랍니다.
그리고 당신도 더 따뜻해질 수 있습니다. 
내 감정이 언젠가 당신에게 닿으면 우리는 서로에게 a shelter 될 것입니다. 

사랑해요 현진이,
당신은 내가 가장 좋아하는 사람입니다.

author: @camcura
text: My mental health has taken a huge hit in the past 110 days since Hyunjin is on hiatus. I sleep 3 hours a day because I fall asleep at 2 am and wake up at 5 am, I run to check my phone to see if there is any news about him and after that I can’t sleep, and this torment has been going on for 110 days. I never had a bias in Stray Kids, I never understood how it is possible to choose one among these guys, so my heart hurts for the whole group and for each individual member, and now it just breaks with pain for Hyunjin. How many more members do we have to lose for the company to understand that fans are also people who find comfort in Stray Kids, but right now this is just a torment for the fans. I can't even imagine what Hyunjin is going through, this uncertainty destroys.

author: @leticiavargas1136
text:
안녕 baby, 어떻게 지내제요?
Have you eat already? 

How are you really doing?
I was thinking... is there something else?
Well, I kind know how time is important for healing.   
I said before, right? I trust you. 
And I'm here. 
I can hold your hand and wait by your side.
You can cry, you can smile, you can make mistakes, you can get things right... I'm with you.
As you're with me, here. 
Miles away, but you're here. 

So, I can be with you, as long as you want.
I'll cry, I'll laugh, I'll make mistakes and I'll get things right... just like you. 

나는 당신을 믿습니다.
그래도 당신이 정말 무슨 일을 겪고 있는지 모르겠어요.
당신은 혼자가 아닙니다. 

나와 이야기 할 수 없다는 건 알지만 .. 필요한 건 뭐든지 ... 신뢰할 수있는 사람과 이야기하세요. 당신을 진정으로 사랑하는 사람에게 의지하십시오.
7 members, 가족과 까미. 

안전하십시오.
유죄로부터 안전하십시오
고통으로부터 안전하십시오
증오로부터 안전하세요
과분한 생각으로부터 안전하십시오
추위로부터 안전
질병으로부터 안전하십시오
모기로부터 안전하십시오
안전하십시오. 

(And smile) 

사랑해요 현이,
나와 함께 당신을위한 안전한 장소가 항상있을 것입니다.
당신은 내가 가장 좋아하는 사람입니다.

author: @leticiavargas1136
text:
어떻게 지내세요 내 현이?
Tomorrow I have a day off work, what should I do?
What are you going to do today?
Can I be with you? 

I would like to watch something funny, any recommendations? 
I avoid watching sad things because I easily cry. (I'm working on that)
Let's just do something fun, ok? 

I heard once that each day we should always be thankful to at least 3 things. Doesn't matter how bad your day was, if you stop to think for a minute you'll have at least 3 things to be thankful. You can pray to say thank you, you can just say it a loud, or write on a diary. What are you grateful for today? 

My to-be-grateful list:
1. I'm glad I can listen to my favorite songs.
2. I'm glad I've safely arrived home.
3. I'm glad Hyunjin exists. 

사랑해요 현진이 
당신은 내가 가장 좋아하는 사람입니다.
나는 우리가 슬픈 순간을 겪을 수 있다는 것을 알고 있지만 당신을 사랑하는 것은 내 인생에서 가장 아름다운 것 중 하나입니다. 

"도망가자
멀리 안 가도 괜찮을 거야
너와 함께라면 난 다 좋아
너의 맘이 편할 수 있는 곳
그게 어디든지 얘기 해줘
...
가보는 거야 달려도 볼까
어디로든 어떻게든
내가 옆에 있을게 마음껏 울어도 돼
그 다음에 

돌아오자 씩씩하게
지쳐도 돼 내가 안아줄게
괜찮아 좀 느려도 천천히 걸어도
나만은 너랑 갈 거야 어디든"

author: @leticiavargas1136
text:
안녕 내 현이, 어떻게 지내세요?

What are you doing?
Are you thinking about us lately? 

Stays took the whole day to send love to you. Have you seen? I hope you've seen it. How much you're precious to them.
I know how stays are important to you.
Can you see it? How important you are to them?
When someone loves us... it's never about if we deserve it or not. People say that love is blind... but I don't think so. I think loves makes us see with our heart. Love makes us feel touched by others. And when it touches us, we feel moved to love. 
We simply fall in love. 
Love makes us see and appreciate a person for who they are.
There's no need of explanation. 

사랑해요 황현진,
Just because.
Just because 황현진 is 황현진. 
And just because you are you.

author: @leticiavargas1136
text:
안녕 현이, 어떻게 지내세요?
Being here... 
It's just because you made through...
You simply got into my system. 
You're here, being part of me somehow.
And,
It's scary, it's terrifying, being here and exposing my thoughts, my feeling, myself...
(I wish you were the only one reading it.)
But it's okay.
It's okay because it's about you, not me. 
I really care.
And maybe I can't explain why I got to this point... but I know it's because of you.
You being you. Just you.
You're the reason. 

And honestly, I should be thanking you for me being here. Living something like this. 
Cause I really love loving you.
Thank you. 
Thank for your smile being so warm.
Thank you for your laugh be so contagious. 
Thank you for your eyes being so bright.
Thank you for your love be so genuine. 
Thank you for your all the time you spend thinking about doing your best. 
Thank you for your voice being so strong and times so sweet.
Thank you for you being the sweetest  funny, warm human being that you are. 

You're just a person.
I know that.
But you're my favorite person. 
사랑해요 현진.

author: @leticiavargas1136
text:
안녕 baby! 어떻게 지내세요? Again, I'm late. I'm so sorry, I'll write on time tomorrow.
But, why do I care so much about writing to you at a specific time?
Well, first of all, I would come either way. (You're part of me, my day and my life.)
The time is because... I really want you to see me as a reliable person... and feel that you can trust me.
I can't do much, and I have few things I can control on "our relationship"... so writing you at night... you receiving every morning... it's nice to "control" that.
Am I being a little crazy?
Is it a bad thing?
I'm sorry again. 

You know I'll be here, right?
Are you doing nice things? 
Hope you trying new things as well. 
Eating well, playing, watching dramas, reading, singing.
Wish to do some of those things with you...
In certain way, you can keep me close to your heart. You can keep this feeling forever if you want. Someone that loves you. I'll always be this someone. 

사랑해요 현이,
당신은 내가 가장 좋아하는 사람입니다.

update : hes back guys, hes home. <\3

author: @leticiavargas1136
text:
안녕 baby, 어떻게 지내세요?
I really don't know where to start today.
It was such a long day... 

Let's go from the top. 

We did it. We won.
We f cking won. God. I still can't believe I was a little part of this process.
Still, the victory it's all yours. 

Every step, every practice, every concert, every moment... every little thing each one of you been through were the reason why you won. And that's why, I'm here to say how proud I am of you. Nothing could take you from being there. You made part of it.
You are part of it. 

I didn't know if I should say that to you or not... but in the end I think I should be honest.
I cried so hard watching the performance... I missed you so damn much... 
I just
I just wish to see your face, and because I know how much you deserve it, I just wanted to see you receiving it. 

I don't wanna cry anymore today so let's just stop right here. 

I love you, you know that, right? 

More than anything I want you to be happy.
So, don't worry about me.
I told you, it's ok miss people we love.
My only concern is you.  

My friend says that both of us seem to be the same person, that we feel things and we think in similar ways. 

I don't know if that's true, but just in case, I wanna feel only good stuff so maybe you could feel good as well. 

How am I feeling?
I'm proud. 
I'm happy because my 8 boys kept fighting.
I'm looking forward for what's next... maybe June will be a good month?
Shall we make a good month together? 

사랑해요 황현진,
진짜 사랑해.
나는 당신을 느낍니다.
당신은 내가 가장 좋아하는 사람입니다.

author: @leticiavargas1136
text:
안녕 baby~~~~
어떻게 지내세요? 

오늘의 계획은 무엇입니까?
화요일은 강렬했지만 모든 것을 할 수있어서 기쁩니다 ...
나는 잘했다. 
당신이 내가 최선을 다하고 싶은 이유입니다.
Shall we keep working together?
By your side, I want to deserve this...
사랑하는 사람을 위해 최선을 다해야합니다.
그래서 저는 사람으로서 계속 발전 할 것을 약속합니다.
나는 당신이 자유롭고 자신감을 갖기를 바랍니다.
나는 당신이 누구를 믿을 수 있는지 인식하고 그때 믿기를 바랍니다.
나는 당신이 항상 사랑 받고 있다고 느끼기를 바랍니다. 

사랑해요 현진이,
당신은 내가 가장 좋아하는 사람입니다.

author: @leticiavargas1136
text:
안녕 baby, 잘 잤어?

너의 하루가 나보다 좋았어? 나는 희망한다.
벌써 먹었어?
벌써 웃었 어?
알겠습니다. 당신은 내가 미소를 지을 때까지 기다리고있었습니다.
그래서 그것을 엽니 다.
지금.
가다.
어서.
웃고 있니? 

웃고있는 네가 생각나서 웃고있어. (그리고 내 어리 석음 때문에)
사람들을 웃게 만들어 ... 당신은이 힘을 가지고 있습니다.
좋은 힘이라고 생각하지 않나요?


그래서 오늘 새 노래가 나왔는데 가사를 읽을 때 ... 너 생각 했어 

"얼음뿐인 이곳에서
넌 유1하게 빛나던 glow
Now I can’t stop thinking bout you
When I’m sinking alone" 

너무 감동적 이었어요 ...
나의 어둠의 세계에서 당신은 따뜻한 빛입니다. 나는 당신이 당신의 세계에서 찾을 수 있기를 바랍니다. 당신을 미소 짓고 따뜻하게 할 수있는 빛 ... 

(The song is 0x1 = Lovesong by TXT) 

사랑해요 현..
당신은 내가 가장 좋아하는 사람입니다.

author: @leticiavargas1136
text:
안녕 baby, 어떻게 지내세요?
이번 주에는 너무 바쁠 것입니다.하지만 걱정하지 마세요. 여기 와서 좀 괴롭힐 게요. 

I was just wishing to my Sunday keep lasting so Monday wouldn't come but...
시간은 앞으로 나아가 야한다. 

Thanks to that this year I met you and I'm here today talking to you. What else time will give us? 

나는 앞으로 좋은 일을 바란다.
나는 당신보다 더 좋은 선물을받을 수 있다고 정말로 믿지 않습니다.
당신도 뭔가를 받았으면 좋겠어요.
Something so good that will make you want to keep it forever.
You're a precious thing that I wanna keep forever. 

And about me, for my next gift... it would be nice to share it with you. 

And I hope to be around and watch time gives you great gifts.
You deserve happiness, nothing less.
(We all do, right?) 

사랑해요 현이,
당신은 내가 가장 좋아하는 사람입니다.

author: @leticiavargas1136
text:
안녕 현진아, 어떻게 지내세요?
그래서 일요일이야! 무엇을하실 건가요? 

오늘 친한 친구로부터 따뜻한 말을 받았습니다. 그의 메시지를 읽었을 때 나는 "아, 말이 너무 따뜻할 수있다"고 생각했고 그것이 나를 미소게 만들었다는 것을 깨달았다.
I wish I could have this power, the power to reach you with warm words and make you smile. 

당신이 그걸 아는지 모르겠지만이 모든 상황 때문에 매일 여기에 오지 않습니다. 

나는 당신과 이야기하는 것을 정말로 좋아하기 때문에 여기에 온다. 그리고 나는 오는 것을 멈추고 싶지 않다... 내가 너무 이상해? 익숙해 지 셨으면 좋겠네요 ㅋㅋㅋ 

나는 당신을 정말로 걱정합니다. 당신이 한 모든 것, 당신이있는 방식 ... 당신은 내 마음에 직접 왔어요. 

감사. 당신이 여기 있다면.
모든 것에 감사드립니다.
당신을 너무 사랑하게 해주셔서 감사합니다.
저를 웃게 해주셔서 감사합니다. (많이 웃습니다)
당신이 누군지 감사합니다. 

I am you.
I see me in you. 

사랑해요 현이,
당신은 내가 가장 좋아하는 사람이야.

author: @swansmi2633
text:
Как прошел твой день? У меня не очень и сейчас я плачу. Кажется так у меня снимается стресс. Становится чуть легче. Как с этим справляешься ты? В любом случае надеюсь, что ты в порядке. Почти каждый день задаю тебе одни и те же вопросы в этих комментариях, иногда жалуюсь, выражаю свою тревогу и беспокойство.. Я ужасно скучаю.. Но почему, я и сама не знаю, всегда возвращаюсь к этому видео в ожидании тебя.. Хотя бы раз в день я должна зайти сюда и поприветствовать тебя, узнать как у тебя дела и вообще.. Я люблю этот твой танец, что ты так усердно для нас готовил и придумывал хореографию.. Я люблю это чувство, что появляется, когда я смотрю на тебя танцующего.. Ты - мое утешение. Ни одной весточки о тебе. Я волнуюсь. Так жестоко. Наверное тебе нужно правильное время для возвращения. Я не виню тебя. Виноваты все, но не ты. Глубокая ночь, а у вас утро. Пусть твой день будет хорошим. Возвращайся скорее.
Всегда жду, твоя Stay.

text:
안녕 baby, 어떻게 지내제요?
지금 무슨 생각을하고 계십니까?
너는 생각하고 있니...

현진이.
나는 당신이 미소를 생각하고 있어요.
그가 미소를 띄게하기 위해 내가 무엇을 말할 수 있을까? 

대체 어딜 간 거야 너의 그 예쁜 미소?
대체 어딜 간 거야? 

If being loved, truly, makes you smile...
지금 당장 미소를 지어야합니다.

author: @J_thewriter18
text: I've only been a stay since September of last year but all 8 of these boys mean so much to me already and especially Hyunjin because he's become one of my comfort idols. I've been going through a lot of stuff recently from fearing the end of my freshman year to my mom being in and out of the hospital and so on, but it's even worse without Hyunjin. I can't even look at a picture of him without breaking down sobbing. His adorable, weird, goofy self makes me smile and yeah I know there's people that will say "oh why not watch an old video of him?", it's just not the same as waking up to a Vlive notification saying he's live or seeing new videos of him or seeing him perform with the other members. When Chan went live on Sunday and it said he had a special guest a part of me was begging for it to be Hyunjin but it wasn't and I was sad. I mean don't get me wrong Chan with a Deadpool mask is funny but I just really miss Hyunjin a lot.

author: @leticiavargas1136
text:
안녕 baby,
I forget my coat today. 
I'm freezing to death here.
I don't know if I'll survive.
Wish me luck. 

When I was a kid, I used to like going through long tunnels. The radio stops and there's this silence. You can't see the end and everyone goes in the same direction. No one stops or slows down. Just keep going. Doesn't matter if it was day or night, inside a tunnel always would look the same.
It seems like for one moment we got disconnected from outside.
And then, the light shines at the end. So bright. Because we were in the dark, the light seems to be more clear than before. 
And we get out. The radio turns on again, you look to the sky and the world is huge again. 

So because of these memories I never compare being in a tunnel with a bad thing.
I guess it could be compare to any moment of your life, you can't just stop living, we need to keep going no matter what. We can't see the end when we began. But we can be sure that if you got in, you'll get out. There's always an way out. You just need to keep moving. 
Like when you're practicing hard to something to come.
When you're studying to pass a exam.
When you're waiting for someone you love.
When you need time to yourself.
We never know what's ahead of us.
It could be great... 

You were one of the brightest light that hit me. 

I'm sure you had plenty of shine bright lights on your way. But if you just keep going, you'll find much more beautiful lights. 

사랑해요 현진이 💛
당신은 내가 가장 좋아하는 사람입니다.

author: @batoulassad6273
text:
Ahem
Dear JYP,
Hello, I have been a STAY for about 4 years, ever since day 1, Hyunjin has been my bias. I don't know why, but I felt something spark inside of me when I saw his smile. I always smile when I see him dancing, he has made me feel alot better about myself. Stray kids as a whole gave me so much hope, but now, not seeing him on stage with the rest of the group breaks my heart. These past few months, I haven't been sleeping well, and my grades aren't at there best. I can't stop thinking about Hyunjin, I miss him so much. I sometimes don't want to eat, my family has even noticed me being different. I love Hyunjin so much, he and Stray kids have been there for me since the start. Not just for me, but for all STAYs. So please bring Hyunjin back, it's almost been 100 days, I want to see him smile, dance, and sing again. I stan 8 amazing boys, not 7.
#BringHyunjinback #OT8
To Hyunjin: 
If you ever get to see my message, know I speak for all STAYs Hyunjin. We all love you and will support you through everything that happens. I will never stop loving you. You're so hardworking and talented. You told STAY you wanted to do better and show us a "Stray kids that won't disappoint us." You have showed us a Stray Kids that is not disappointing. Thank you so much for being there for me and for all STAYs! My love for you and all of Stray kids can't be explained in words. You are my world, my happiness, my support, and my role models. Thank you. Thank you for everything you do. I love you, please don't forget it! <3

Edit: Thank you for taking the time to read my letter! <3 :]

author: @swansmi2633
text:
Несправедливо. Вот такое чувство. Опустошение и печаль.. будто упоминать тебя, писать о тебе, говорить что в таком-то выступлении тебя не хватило - это неправильно. Разве этим я пыталась бы обесценить труд Стрей Кидс? Разве Хенджин не Стрей Кидс? Разве я не могу выражать свои чувства от его отсутствия и тосковать? Почему он как табу.. Почему все должны привыкать к его отсутствию и молча терпеть словно его с ними никогда и не было. Так некоторые бейби стей уверены, что Стрей семеро. Когда он вернется, он ведь не станет чужим для них? Он ведь тоже должен им понравиться? Несправедливо. Как для Хенджина, так и для ждущих его. Я слишком чувствительна? Я беспокоюсь, волнуюсь, переживаю без новостей о нем и тем больше проходит времени тем больше возрастает и накапливается все во мне, что кажется еще чуть-чуть и я взорвусь! Несправедливо было так поступать с ним, с нами. Несправедливо затыкать тех, кто волнуется о нем...  Несправедливо говорить, что и без Хенджина они прекрасно справились, тем самым подразумевая, что что есть он или нет его - никакой разницы, ущемляя его как мембра. Приятно было бы вам, если бы вы узнали, что люди говорят что и без вашего участия ваша команда справилась. Разве вы не почувствовали себя разъединенной от всех остальных и не нужной? Какая разница, верно? Почему Хенджинни должен быть на задворках, где-то в стороне.. Несправедливо. Виню ли я в этом Стреев? Нет. Я им верю и верю, что они поддерживают Хенджина как могут. Но больше я никому не верю, включая джуп и его стаф, клио, мнет и "Стей" у которых одно только название, если они не переживают за каждого из мембов. 
Все еще жду каждый день. Надеюсь, что ничто из этого не коснется наших мальчиков.. Любите и будьте любимы. Ждите и пусть всегда дожидаются вас.

text: Hyunjin, my angel .. good morning! Like all good music, you still make me want to dance, I think of you all the time like I'm playing every time the song is over. author: @leticiavargas1136
text:
안녕 baby, 어떻게 지내제요? 

When I was thinking in what to tell you today... the word "enjoy" kept coming.
You know English is not my native language as well, so, since I learned the meaning of "enjoy" until now, it became one of my favorites words in English. 

Enjoy.
Enjoy it.
Enter joy. 
Let joy enter. 

I know we can't have joyfull days everyday. That doesn't mean we have to stop enjoying.
Enjoy is about seeing the good things we have at the moment and appreciate it.
Don't let many days pass without enjoying it. Joy is not something to achieve, is something to notice. 

사랑해요 현진이,
당신는 내가 가장 좋아하는 사람입니다.

author: @leticiavargas1136
text:
친애하는 현진,
좋은 일요일을 보내.
풍토로 인해 기분이 바뀌지 마십시오.
그리고 제발, 당신의 시간과 자신을 즐기십시오.
자신에게 너무 가혹하지 마십시오.
나는 우리가 최악의 적이 될 수 있다고 생각하는 경향이 있습니다.
당신의 경우가 아니길 정말 바래요
당신의 경우가 아니기를 정말로 바랍니다.
어떻게 된 건지는 모르겠지만... 여기 내 마음 속에 당신이 느껴집니다.
나는 당신을 보호 할 수 없습니다. 내가 얼마나 원하는지는 중요하지 않습니다.
동시에 나는 당신이 그것을 할 수 있다고 전적으로 믿습니다. 당신은 용감합니다. 너가 그런걸 난 알아.
나는 당신이 다치는 것을 압니다. 그리고 아마도 당신은 지금 다칠지도 모릅니다 ...
강한 사람이된다는 것은 결코 다 치지 않는다는 의미가 아닙니다.
강한 사람은 단호하고 절대 포기하지 않고 일어 선다.
나는 당신이 얼마나 강한 지 진정으로 믿습니다. 솔직히 당신을 믿습니다.
자신의 신념, 원칙, 자신이 누구인지 의심하지 마십시오
현진, 네가 너무 자랑스러워.
내가 당신을 소유한다고 생각해서가 아닙니다.
당신 같은 사람을 사랑하게 된 것을 자랑스럽게 생각합니다. 

사랑해요 현진이, 
당신은 내가 가장 좋아하는 사람입니다..

author: @swansmi2633
text:
Ах.. это сводит меня с ума.. я так обеспокоена, немного взбудоражена и нетерпелива.. кажется что еще чуть-чуть и я взорвусь от эмоций.. когда же ты вернешься? Нельзя позволять себе плакать и вообще.. я ужасно скучаю. Знаешь, только сейчас я вдруг подумала о том, как ты был так взбудоражен и взволнован перед началом кингдома и просил нас не волноваться. Ты был в предвкушении различных выступлений, но все вот так оборвалось и .. случилось то, что случилось. Могу ли представить себе то, что ты тогда чувствовал? На врядли. Могу ли я утешить тебя? Тот же ответ. Произошедшего не изменить, но я практически уверена, что все было к лучшему. Возможно ты кое-что потерял, но и приобрел немало. 
Я ведь уже говорила, что скучаю? Ужасно скучаю. Вернись побыстрее, наше солнце.
Твоя Stay.

author: @MsMaurity
text: Hello, hyunjin, I'm here, you know? All the time, every day, waiting for you. Sitting in front of my cell phone, with a huge smile on my face, wanting to tell you everything I keep in me. Would being grateful to have you here would be enough? No, I know I don't. And for your smiles that make me smile? .... no. So, I stayed here, thinking about what to say. Always try to smile, even in the face of difficulties and do not be ashamed of tears. Even though it is difficult, never stop believing in yourself, in your ability and in a tomorrow where you will be happier. Don't let yourself be overwhelmed by difficulties, do not let yourself be overcome by discouragement. Everything comes and one day it goes away; the important thing is to keep hope and keep fighting, love is the greatest strength you have. Believe in yourself, in your strength. I know that you can, that you can. I am and will always be here. I'm not going anywhere.

author: @leticiavargas1136
text:
안녕 baby, 잘 지내?
잘 잤기를 바래.
주말이 다가 왔습니다. 어떻게해야합니까? 

오늘 당신이 저에게 한 일에 대해 감사드립니다.
요즘 일은 쉽지 않습니다.
당신이 어떤지 모르겠어요.
그러나 나는 일이 쉽지 않다고 말할 수 있습니다.
나에게는 아니야. 

그러나 당신은...
당신은 내 생각과 내 마음에 존재합니다.
나는 항상 여기서 당신에게 더 강한 사람이되는 것을 생각합니다.
신뢰할 수 있고 더 긍정적 인 사람이됩니다.
나는 당신이 나를 의지 할 수 있기를 원하기 때문에 더 강해지고 싶습니다. 

그리고 일어났습니다.
나는 일어나서 다시 힘을 얻었다.
나를위한 힘, 당신을위한 힘.
감사합니다. 원하는만큼 여기에 살 수 있습니다.
나는 떠날 필요가 없도록 충분히 강해지겠다고 약속합니다. 

사랑해요 현진이, 
당신은 내가 가장 좋아하는 사람입니다.

author: @itsnlee
text:
According to his comment in the description, I translated it using a site: 

"I made the choreography of this song, recalling when it was the hardest time for me. First of all, I chose this song because I was looking for a song that best suits these three topics: emptiness, hopelessness, longing. The emptiness at the end of a party is like the loneliness of returning home, missing it after taking the big stage. Because I thought it was emotion.I tried to express my feelings as much as I could, and I hope it was delivered."

author: @leticiavargas1136
text:
안녕 baby, 어제 좋은 하루 보냈어? 

음, 오늘 제가하고 싶은 말은 ...
지금은 별이 보이지 않습니다.
하늘이 너무 어둡다.
별은 항상 내가 혼자가 아닌 것처럼 느끼게 만듭니다.
어떻게해야합니까?
가끔은 우리 모두 혼자 있어야 할 것 같아요. 심지어 별.
별처럼 우리는 시간을 가져야합니다. 그들이 우리를 버린 것과는 다릅니다.
우리는 그것을 압니다.
날씨가 좋으면 별이 다시 올 것입니다. 

우리는 그것과 다르지 않습니까? 

조만간 현진이 좋은 기후를 찾길 바랍니다. 

사랑해 황현진, 
넌 내가 제일 좋아하는 사람이야.

I made the choreography for this song reminding me of the most difficult times.

text:
안녕 baby, 어떻게 지내세요?
겁내지 마세요.
나는 당신을 믿습니다.
걱정이 당신의 생각과 감정을 지배하게하지 마십시오. 나는 당신이 결코 다 치지 않을 것이라고 말할 수 없습니다 (불행히도). 그러나 확실히 당신은 항상 당신 곁에 당신을 사랑하는 사람들이있을 것입니다. (또는 여기) 

결론은: 만약 내가 여기 있기 위해 상처를 입어야한다면... 괜찮습니다.
이 글을 읽고 기분이 나아질 가능성이있는 한 괜찮습니다. 

내가 다쳐도 괜찮아.. 너 때문에.
그러니 현진이 도중에 다쳤어도... 괜찮 으면 좋겠는데... 누군가가 널 사랑 하니까.

당신은 내가 가장 좋아하는 사람입니다.

text:
안녕 baby, 어떻게 지내세요?

오늘은 일하고 공부하면서 많은 노래를 듣습니다. 내가 당신에게 노래를 보내고 싶었 기 때문입니다.
너무 힘들 었어요. 보내고 싶은 노래가 너무 많아요.
사실 그 문제가 있습니다... 저는 앨범을 좋아해서 풀 앨범을 추천하고 싶습니다. 하지만 이런 음악을 듣는 데 익숙한 지 모르겠습니다.So 

많은 경이로움 끝에 하나를 찾았습니다. (그리고 앨범은 내가 가장 좋아하는 것 중 하나입니다)
Wonder by Eric Nam... 가사는 내가 당신에 대해 올바른 방식으로 생각하게 만들었습니다...

author: @leticiavargas1136
text:
안녕 baby, 잘 지내?
주말! 
서울이 더워 진다고 들었는데 여기가 추워지고 있어요... 

하지만 지금 날씨가 더워지고 있는데 내 말이 따뜻하지 않고 상쾌 할까? 

어떤 단어가 상쾌합니까?
안도감을 느끼게하는 말?
걱정을 없애는 말? 

황현진, 말해봐 지금 고민은 뭐야? 

이해해 ... 

내가 생각하는 한, 아무도 당신에게 실망하지 않습니다. STAYS가 당신을 다시 보는 것보다 더 원하는 것은 없습니다. 모두가 당신과 영원히 함께하겠다고 약속했듯이 그들은 떠나지 않았습니다. STAYS는 당신과 함께 있습니다. 

당신도 STAYS를 사랑합니까?
Is it a good feeling when who you love, loves you back? 

우리에 대해 계속 생각하면 우리는 당신에 대해 계속 생각할 것입니다. 

사랑해요 현진이,
당신은 내가 가장 좋아하는 사람입니다.

Ps. (가을을 그리워하면 내 가을을 빌릴 수 있습니다)

text:
For those who have sparks in their eyes,
For those who smile is like the sunlight,
For those which voice make your heart beat faster,
For those who by dancing create a new whole universe,

For those who can make you laugh,

For those who can make you feel "like a pshyco",

author: @swansmi2633
text:
В каждом шаге Стрей Кидс вижу тебя.. Сегодня я отчаянно желала бы увидеть тебя в танцевальном юните на кингдом.. Я хотела бы наблюдать как ты репетируешь, веселишься, выступаешь и заводишь новые знакомства как это сейчас делают Стрей.. Почему я чувствую такую потерю?.. Я уверена, что одна твоя улыбка покорила бы всех.. Иногда меня одолевает тревога за тебя. Вдруг ты потерял уверенность и веру, вдруг разочарован, вдруг ... ах как много этих вдруг и что если... Я стараюсь быть оптимистичной и верить в то, что с тобой все в порядке и нет поводов для беспокойств. Но я не могу временами.. Как ты себя чувствуешь? Почему я спрашиваю об этом в пустоту... Хенджин, временами я сомневаюсь в том, что делаю. И хочу все стереть, будто этого никогда и не было. Но не со всем это возможно сделать. И иногда в определенные моменты эти воспоминания и последствия возвращаются. И я опять сгораю и хочу провалиться сквозь землю, чтобы больше не чувствовать того, что приносит дискомфорт.. Но мне приходиться просто идти дальше, ведь пути назад нет и делать вид, что меня не волнует.. Ничего не волнует. 
Знаешь, люди очень редко когда замечают, что ты разбит и склеен по кусочкам пока ты им об этом не скажешь. Даже если и скажешь редко кто воспримет всерьез и услышит. Возможно я такая же. И от этого погано. Но оставаться в таком состоянии одному еще поганее.. Я надеюсь, что ты окружен людьми, которые воспринимают тебя всерьез и ценят твое доверие. Не оставайся один на один со своими проблемами и страхами, ведь так они кажутся значимее, чем возможно они есть. 
У тебя утро. Проведи этот день на позитиве, а я пойду спать, чтобы проснуться, когда у вас будет примерно полдень. Хорошего тебе дня.
Твоя Stay.

author: @MsMaurity
text:
내 사랑 현진, 오늘은 노래를 추천합니다.

Le canzoni non si scrivono
Ma nascono da se
Son le cose che succedono
Ogni giorno intorno a noi

Le canzoni basta coglierle
C'è ne una anche per te
Che fai più fatica a vivere
E non sorridi mai

Le canzoni sono zingare
E rubano poesie
Sono iganni come pilole
Della felicità

Le canzoni non guariscono
Amori e malattie
Ma quel piccolo dolore
Che l'esistere ci da

Passerà, passerà
Se un ragazzo e una chitarra sono lì
Come te, in città
A guardare questa vita che non va
Che ci ammazza d'illusioni
E con l'età delle canzoni

Passerà su di noi
Finiremo tutti in banca prima o poi
Coi perchè, i chissà
E le angoscie di una ricca povertà
A parlare degli amori che non hai
A cantare una canzone che non sai come fa
Perchè l'hai perduta dentro
E ti ricordi solamente
Passerà

In un mondo di automobili
E di gran velocità
Per chi arriva sempre ultimo
E per chi si dice addio
Per chi sbatte negli ostacoli
Della diversità
Le canzoni sono lucciole
Che cantano nel buio

Passerà prima o poi
Questo piccolo dolore
Che c'è in te, che c'è in me, che c'è in noi
E ci fa sentire come marinai
In balia del vento e della nostalgia
A cantare una canzone che no sai come fa
Ma quel piccolo dolore
Che sia odio, o che sia amore
Passerà

Passerà, passerà
Anche se farai soltanto
La la la
Passerà, passerà
E a qualcosa una canzone servirà
Se il tuo piccolo dolore
Che sia odio, o che sia amore
Passerà

PASSERA (통과 할 것이다)
RENATO RUSSO (레나토 루소)

author: @leticiavargas1136
text:
안녕 baby, 잘 잤어?
평소처럼 버스를 기다리고 있습니다. 더 두꺼운 코트를 가져 왔지만 오늘은 더 추워요. 어떻게? ㅠㅠ 

I had this bad feeling all day long, I really hope you're ok. Hope is a good word, isn't it? 
I always say that I hope this and that...
I think because hope can keep us moving,  like the flow of a river. As long you're inside, if you let it drive you, it can take you anywhere.
Hope is not a silly thing. 
Hope is not sit and wait.
Hope is believe, trust and act. 

That's why I keep hoping.
And I keep coming. 
To say that I hope you're ok, I hope you're healthy, I hope you're warm, I hope you're still having a good time and eating nice things. I hope you're doing things you like. I hope you can feel lighter each day. I hope you can feel how much you're loved. I hope you know that if I love you... it's because you are you.  

Can my acts of hope reach you? 

사랑해 황현진. 
당신은 내가 가장 좋아하는 사람입니다.

author: @duckgu_sim
text:
현지나 머해? 
요즘 계속 매일 모오게되는거 같아가지구 미안하다 ㅠ_ㅠ
계속 퇴근해서 씻구 누워서 얼른써야지 하구 폰키면 바로 기절해가지구
슬럼프인디 일은또 넘 바빠가지고 
완전 잠으로 도피수준으로 무의식으로 빠지는거 같아 푸_푸 
그래도 꼬옥 현진이 맨날맨날 생각하구 보고 싶구 
기다리고오 역시 하루에 끝에 현진이 찾아오고 싶어서 시간을 
퇴근시간 이후 밤쯤으로 한건데 
시간날 때 찾아오는거로 바꿔야 할까 싶기두 하구 ㅠㅠ 

근데 또 그렇게 되면 너무 짧게 현진아 머해?하고만 적어둘 것 같애,,
출근해서 넘 여러 일들이 많이 생겨가지구,,
요즘 현진이는 어때?

author: @leticiavargas1136
text:
안녕 baby, 오늘의 계획은 무엇입니까?

I was thinking about what to tell you today but words were missing...
Probably because I miss you so much...
And I don't say that everyday because I don’t know how you feel about it...
But it's true. I miss you and I miss you and I miss you. You're my favorite person. For real. 

Please don't feel bad. 
You know that already, right?
That I miss you like crazy? 

You miss like crazy stays as well, don't you?
I know babe.
It's ok to miss people we love that much.
And a love like yours... It's so warm and beautiful... How not to miss that? 

Things happen for a reason. 
I'll keep praying for this warm feelings come to you. 
Hate could be a huge thing sometimes and sadness it's a feeling that we all feel when in difficult times.
But, if you have love (and you do), love is even bigger and even stronger.
Love it's precious and not that easy to find. 
You're a piece of love, as you are.
We have flaws, but love never fails.
I trust in you. 
And even though I'm scared as hell with this amount of love I feel, I don't care. It's yours.
You have it. You have my love, my care, my thoughts, my prayers. 
I'll be here. 

사랑해요 현진이,
당신은 내가 가장 좋아하는 사람입니다.

Ps. Guess I found the words ㅋㅋㅋ

author: @tahe6240
text:
I'm not really sure if you'll see this, but i hope you do. I wanted you to know that we will wait for you no matter how much time passes. Our fandom's name is the reasom why. We're Stay. We're staying.
But there's no lie on us saying that we miss you so much, honey.
Even if the guys are doing well, all of us know that it's not the same, and it will never be the same without you. We need you. We miss you. We love you. We need our Lovestay boy. You are like our secret weapon at this point hdjsdj, you are our most talented dancer. Please don't ever doubt about the love we have for you. You are so, so loved. I can't imagine Stray Kids without you in the future. I need you to stay. You guys are a team, a family. Don't ever leave us, sweetie. I beg you.
Our purest and honest boy, we're here. We won't go anywhere, because we made a promise and we'll keep it.
You're my safe place, Hyunjin. Please let us be yours too.
You've helped me through so much this past months, you woke up a side of me I'd never thought I would want again. Everything you have done for Stay and Stray Kids, your loved ones... you're such a good person, Jinnie. You need to know that. Even Channie told us on vlive, because everyone knows it.
I hope we can get some news about you soon. If you don't feel ready to come back yet, it's okay, we will wait. We just want to know if you're okay.
Are you still taking your half baths? Do you need songs reccomendations? Did you find another r&b song you like a lot? Are you learning new dance moves? We just want to know how you're doing.
I love you, Hyunjin.
Everything could be a mess, but the thought of you coming back one day, makes my heart feel a bit better. Come home whenever you feel ready. As long as you're okay, we will be too.
See you soon, dumpling.
I'll keep doing this until the day yo come back, because i miss you too much.
Tahe's note: seeing you dancing will forever be one of my favorite parts of my day.

author: @swansmi2633
text:
Хенджинни... Время все летит и летит... Для меня оно всегда течет быстро, но почему то это не работает с тобой. Я увязла в ожидании тебя. Уже почти что лето, верно? А тогда был снег. Помню как вытирала слезы, читая новости. Ты не заслужил всего плохого, что они о тебе писали. Наверное ты тоже был обескуражен, зол и расстроен.. 
Как ты сейчас? Наверное в начале тебе было непривычно, но позже ты возможно нашел и положительные стороны этой ситуации. Надеюсь ты не погрузился и не погряз в самобичевании и меланхолии. А если такое произошло, то надеюсь, что твои друзья и близкие пинками вывели тебя из такого болота. Знаешь ли, иногда такие "пинки" и "подзатыльники" полезны. Они мгновенно проясняют голову и освежают мировозрение.. Может завтра ты вернешься? Может на следующей неделе? Может через месяц? Через два? Ты обязательно вернешься в камбек. Верно? А он будет этим летом. Эта мысль греет мое сердце. А если этого не случится, то все будет разбито.. Так что не подводи меня пожалуйста. Я не хочу локальной трагедии в моем мире и огромной трагедии Стей. Просто возвращайся так, будто и не уходил. Просто напиши нам, что скучал, а мы в ответ, что тоже.
Твоя Stay.

author: @sammm.roldan
text:
mi vida, no sabes la falta que me haces, realmente te extraño como nunca extrañé a nadie... me duele en el alma no poder saber nada de vos, cómo te sentís, si comiste, si descansaste, si dormiste bien, si necesitás un abrazo, si leíste algún libro o jugaste con kkami. Hay días que realmente me siento cansada, nadie se da cuenta de lo mal que me siento por tu ausencia, ni aunque lo demuestre no hay alguien que me pregunte cómo estoy, ni me dan ánimos, me siento más sola que nunca y no tengo a mi lugar seguro para sentirme mejor... siento que no tengo a la razón que le daba sentido a mi vida, que me quitaron al ser que más amo en este maldito mundo, de momentos siento que me quiero rendir, pero recuerdo tu hermosa sonrisa que tanto amo, y solo quiero seguir para volver a verte y ser tan inmensamente feliz otra vez. 
Te voy a estar esperando mi hermoso angelito... solo espero que te encuentres bien.♡
